me/freehongkonghkg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/nBMTNBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBMTNBB.jpg&h=16392072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n讓這攬炒旗隨風飄揚！（logo已獲攬炒巴授權使用）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人哋北韓都做到 香港唔係做唔到呀嘛？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共已經決定企硬，連溫和到咁既五大訴求都唔會接受。咁呢個政府仲有咩面代表人民<br />\n<br />\n擇個好日子揀個好地方，設立海外臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n目標係「要使國際社會廣泛相信港共政府為非法政權，爭取外國政府支持，替天行道，天滅中共」<br />\n「因應警察濫用暴力+濫捕事件於國際組織上追究」<br />\n<br />\n最後「推動香港進入real autonomy 嘅時代」<br />\n<br />\n因為而家我哋已經無嘢可以好輸，如果我哋就咁俾場運動完結，最後受害，被批鬥，被清算係每一個真。香港人。前線於是，和理非也如是。警察已經將文革係各中小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"ffa3cadb7031ab6aa4fbe6637071a740fad9881c","tid":1567332,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b3c6232a2a5ded82012a6b39fcf2178d0d1628b","tid":1567332,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 811 831</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"06df426aea36e380a11d3f4b3fa9fa0632b2f38a","tid":1567332,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e377aa7ecca98f1e7f57580e644604bce289ce3f","tid":1567332,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"約左民主女神行街"},{"pid":"34e192c8db4f7917a0df7eb355e63dc3eae30ae2","tid":1567332,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"時代門外再聚"},{"pid":"11e191473b1a7611fbe1919ebef55ecdc00eecf7","tid":1567332,"uid":217990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"行街睇戲食飯"},{"pid":"0fe21d418d1b06cc87a594440c9f78